msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ADVENTURE_PORTAL"
msgid "I'm not sure I want to fall for that a second time."
msgstr "Bunun tuzağına ikinci kez düşmek istediğimden emin değilim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIANHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIANHAT"
msgid "It shows me infinite possibilities..."
msgstr "Bana sonsuz olasılıkları gösteriyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIANHATSHARD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIANHATSHARD"
msgid "Even a single piece is pretty illuminating!"
msgstr "Tek parçası bile epey aydınlatıcı!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_CONTAINED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_CONTAINED"
msgid "It's draining the energy right out of that monster!"
msgstr "Tam o canavarın enerjisini emiyor!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE1.DEAD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE1.DEAD"
msgid "Gotcha!"
msgstr "Yakaladım!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE1.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE1.GENERIC"
msgid "You'll pay for breaking all that science!"
msgstr "Tüm o bilimi parçaladığının bedelini ödeyeceksin!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE1_LUNARRIFT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE1_LUNARRIFT"
msgid "You look the same but different."
msgstr "Aynı ama farklı görünüyorsun."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE1_LUNARRIFT_GESTALT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE1_LUNARRIFT_GESTALT"
msgid "This must be the one he wants."
msgstr "Onun istediği bu olmalı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE2.DEAD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE2.DEAD"
msgid "This time I'm sure I got it."
msgstr "Bu sefer kesinlikle hakladım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE2.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE2.GENERIC"
msgid "I think I just made it angry..."
msgstr "Sanırım onu kızdırdım..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE2SPIKE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE2SPIKE"
msgid "You've made your point!"
msgstr "Sivri noktanı koydun!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE3"
msgid "It's definitely angry now!"
msgstr "Şimdi kesinlikle kızgın!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE3DEAD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE3DEAD"
msgid "Maybe someone should go poke it... just to be sure."
msgstr "Birisi gidip dürtmeli... emin olmak için."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE3DEADORB
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE3DEADORB"
msgid "Is it dead? That strange energy still seems to be lingering around it."
msgstr "Öldü mü? Garip enerji hâlâ etrafında dolaşıyor gibi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE3TRAP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE3TRAP"
msgid "After rigorous testing, I can confirm that they make me want to take a nap."
msgstr "Titiz testlerden sonra şunu doğrulayabilirim: bunlar bende kestirme isteği uyandırıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE4_LUNARRIFT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ALTERGUARDIAN_PHASE4_LUNARRIFT"
msgid "Haven't you broken enough science?!"
msgstr "Yeterince bilimi parçalamadın mı?!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.AMULET
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.AMULET"
msgid "I feel so safe when I get to wear it."
msgstr "Onu taktığımda kendimi çok güvende hissediyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCHOR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCHOR"
msgid "I wouldn't want my boat to float away."
msgstr "Teknemin yüzüp gitmesini istemem."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCHOR_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCHOR_ITEM"
msgid "Now I can build an anchor."
msgstr "Şimdi çapa yapabilirim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTFRUIT_GEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTFRUIT_GEM"
msgid "Hot and fresh off the tree."
msgstr "Ağaçtan sıcak ve taze."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTFRUIT_NIGHTVISION
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTFRUIT_NIGHTVISION"
msgid "I just wish it was less... twitchy."
msgstr "Keşke daha az... seyirseydi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTFRUIT_NIGHTVISION_COOKED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTFRUIT_NIGHTVISION_COOKED"
msgid "At least it stopped twitching."
msgstr "En azından seğirmeyi bıraktı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTTREE_GEM.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTTREE_GEM.GENERIC"
msgid "It's vegetable AND mineral. Fascinating."
msgstr "Hem sebze HEM mineral. Büyüleyici."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTTREE_GEM.STUMP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTTREE_GEM.STUMP"
msgid "This tree has been mined."
msgstr "Bu ağaç madene çevrilmiş."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTTREE_NIGHTVISION.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTTREE_NIGHTVISION.GENERIC"
msgid "Tree-t with caution."
msgstr "Ağaç-ıkkat ile yaklaş."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTTREE_NIGHTVISION.STUMP
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTTREE_NIGHTVISION.STUMP"
msgid "It's a stump."
msgstr "Bir kütük."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTTREE_SAPLING.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTTREE_SAPLING.GENERIC"
msgid "It's growing! I think?"
msgstr "Büyüyor! Sanırım?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTTREE_SAPLING.WRONG_SEASON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTTREE_SAPLING.WRONG_SEASON"
msgid "It seems like it fits in, but it's not yet ready to grow."
msgstr "Yere uyuyor gibi, ama henüz büyümeye hazır değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTTREE_SAPLING.WRONG_TILE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTTREE_SAPLING.WRONG_TILE"
msgid "I don't think it's getting the required nutrients here."
msgstr "Burada gereken besinleri aldığını sanmıyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTTREE_SAPLING_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTTREE_SAPLING_ITEM"
msgid "I need to plant this in the right place."
msgstr "Bunu doğru yere ekmeliyim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTTREE_SEED
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENTTREE_SEED"
msgid "There are no surprises, only incomplete data."
msgstr "Sürpriz yoktur, sadece eksik veri vardır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENT_ALTAR
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENT_ALTAR"
msgid "An ancient and mysterious structure."
msgstr "Kadim ve gizemli bir yapı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENT_ALTAR_BROKEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENT_ALTAR_BROKEN"
msgid "This seems to be broken."
msgstr "Bozulmuş gibi görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENT_HUSK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENT_HUSK"
msgid "Something bad happened here."
msgstr "Burada kötü bir şey olmuş."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENT_STATUE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANCIENT_STATUE"
msgid "It seems to throb out of tune with the world."
msgstr "Dünyayla uyumsuz biçimde titrediğini görüyorum."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANIMAL_TRACK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANIMAL_TRACK"
msgid "Tracks left by food. I mean... an animal."
msgstr "Yiyeceğin bıraktığı izler. Yani... bir hayvanın."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANTCHOVIES
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANTCHOVIES"
msgid "Yeesh. Can I toss it back?"
msgstr "Iyy. Geri atabilir miyim?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANTLION.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANTLION.GENERIC"
msgid "It wants something from me."
msgstr "Benden bir şey istiyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANTLION.UNHAPPY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANTLION.UNHAPPY"
msgid "It looks mad."
msgstr "Kızgın görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANTLION.VERYHAPPY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANTLION.VERYHAPPY"
msgid "I think we're on good terms."
msgstr "Sanırım aramız iyi."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANTLIONHAT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANTLIONHAT"
msgid "It's a groundbreaking scientific achievement."
msgstr "Çığır açan, yer kıran bir bilimsel başarı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANTLIONTRINKET
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ANTLIONTRINKET"
msgid "Someone might be interested in this."
msgstr "Birisi bununla ilgilenebilir."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_CENTIPEDE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_CENTIPEDE"
msgid "You won't centimpede my progress!"
msgstr "Yüz-engel olamazsın bana!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_CENTIPEDE_HUSK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_CENTIPEDE_HUSK"
msgid "A pile of old spare parts."
msgstr "Eski yedek parçalar yığını."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_COOKPOT.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_COOKPOT.BURNT"
msgid "The pot got cooked."
msgstr "Tencere pişti."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_COOKPOT.COOKING_LONG
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_COOKPOT.COOKING_LONG"
msgid "This is going to take a while."
msgstr "Bu biraz zaman alacak."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_COOKPOT.COOKING_SHORT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_COOKPOT.COOKING_SHORT"
msgid "It's almost done!"
msgstr "Neredeyse hazır!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_COOKPOT.DONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_COOKPOT.DONE"
msgid "Mmmmm! It's ready to eat!"
msgstr "Mmmmm! Yenmeye hazır!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_COOKPOT.EMPTY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_COOKPOT.EMPTY"
msgid "Let's dust off this old crockery, shall we?"
msgstr "Şu eski tencerenin tozunu alalım, olur mu?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_LOCKBOX
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_LOCKBOX"
msgid "Now how do I get the knowledge out?"
msgstr "Şimdi bilgiyi nasıl çıkarırım?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_LOCKBOX_DISPENCER.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_LOCKBOX_DISPENCER.GENERIC"
msgid "I have the strongest urge to stand around it and talk about nothing in particular."
msgstr "İçimde etrafında durup havadan sudan konuşma dürtüsü var, en güçlü dürtü."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_LOCKBOX_DISPENCER.POWEROFF
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_LOCKBOX_DISPENCER.POWEROFF"
msgid "If only there was a way to get it working again..."
msgstr "Keşke bunu yeniden çalıştırmanın bir yolu olsa..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_MOON_STATUE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_MOON_STATUE"
msgid "These magnificent moon statues have me waxing poetic."
msgstr "Bu muhteşem ay heykelleri beni dolunay-vari şiirsel kılıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_ORCHESTRINA_MAIN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_ORCHESTRINA_MAIN"
msgid "It's like they made it puzzling on purpose."
msgstr "Sanki kasıtlı olarak bulmaca gibi yapmışlar."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_PORTAL.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_PORTAL.GENERIC"
msgid "Strange, the power is on but this isn't."
msgstr "Tuhaf, güç açık ama bu değil."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_PORTAL.POWEROFF
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_PORTAL.POWEROFF"
msgid "Dead as a dead doornail."
msgstr "Kazık kadar ölü."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_RESONATOR.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_RESONATOR.GENERIC"
msgid "Why use a map when you could use a mind-bogglingly complex piece of machinery?"
msgstr "Mantığı zorlayan karmaşıklıkta bir makine varken neden harita kullanasın?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_RESONATOR.IDLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_RESONATOR.IDLE"
msgid "It seems to have found everything worth finding."
msgstr "Bulmaya değer her şeyi bulmuş gibi görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_RESONATOR_ITEM
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_RESONATOR_ITEM"
msgid "Aha! I used the secret knowledge to build a device! Why does this feel familiar..."
msgstr "Aha! Gizli bilgiyi kullanarak bir aygıt yaptım! Neden bu tanıdık geliyor..."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_RUNE_STATUE.LINE_1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_RUNE_STATUE.LINE_1"
msgid "So much knowledge, if only I could read it!"
msgstr "O kadar çok bilgi, keşke okuyabilseydim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_RUNE_STATUE.LINE_2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_RUNE_STATUE.LINE_2"
msgid "These markings look different from the ones in the rest of the ruins."
msgstr "Bu işaretler harabenin geri kalanındakilerden farklı görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_RUNE_STATUE.LINE_3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_RUNE_STATUE.LINE_3"
msgid "So much knowledge, if only I could read it!"
msgstr "O kadar çok bilgi, keşke okuyabilseydim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_RUNE_STATUE.LINE_4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_RUNE_STATUE.LINE_4"
msgid "These markings look different from the ones in the rest of the ruins."
msgstr "Bu işaretler harabenin geri kalanındakilerden farklı görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_RUNE_STATUE.LINE_5
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_RUNE_STATUE.LINE_5"
msgid "So much knowledge, if only I could read it!"
msgstr "O kadar çok bilgi, keşke okuyabilseydim!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_SECURITY_DESK.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_SECURITY_DESK.GENERIC"
msgid "It looks inviting."
msgstr "Davetkâr görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_SECURITY_DESK.POWEROFF
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_SECURITY_DESK.POWEROFF"
msgid "Whatever it did, it's not doing it anymore."
msgstr "Ne yapıyorsa, artık yapmıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_SECURITY_PULSE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_SECURITY_PULSE"
msgid "Where are you going? Someplace interesting?"
msgstr "Nereye gidiyorsun? İlginç bir yere mi?"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_SWITCH.GEMS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_SWITCH.GEMS"
msgid "The socket is empty."
msgstr "Yuva boş."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_SWITCH.VALID
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARCHIVE_SWITCH.VALID"
msgid "Those gems seem to power it... through entirely scientific means, I'm sure."
msgstr "O cevherler ona güç veriyor gibi... tamamen bilimsel yollarla, eminim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMORDRAGONFLY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMORDRAGONFLY"
msgid "Hot mail!"
msgstr "Sıcak zırh-postası!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMORDREADSTONE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMORDREADSTONE"
msgid "Lightweight, sturdy, and snazzy!"
msgstr "Hafif, sağlam ve şık!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMORGRASS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMORGRASS"
msgid "Hopefully there aren't any bugs in it."
msgstr "Umarım içinde böcek yoktur."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMORMARBLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMORMARBLE"
msgid "That looks really heavy."
msgstr "Gerçekten ağır görünüyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMORRUINS
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMORRUINS"
msgid "It's oddly light."
msgstr "Tuhaf biçimde hafif."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMORSKELETON
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMORSKELETON"
msgid "No bones about it."
msgstr "Bunda bir kemik şüphem yok."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMORSLURPER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMORSLURPER"
msgid "A soggy, sustaining, succulent suit."
msgstr "Sırılsıklam, sağlamlaştırıcı, sulu süs."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMORSNURTLESHELL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMORSNURTLESHELL"
msgid "It sticks to your back when you wear it."
msgstr "Giydiğinde sırtına yapışıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMORWAGPUNK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMORWAGPUNK"
msgid "Fearsome and gearsome."
msgstr "Korkutucu ve dişli."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMORWOOD
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMORWOOD"
msgid "That is a perfectly reasonable piece of clothing."
msgstr "Bu tamamen makul bir kıyafet parçası."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMOR_BRAMBLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMOR_BRAMBLE"
msgid "The best offense is a good defense."
msgstr "En iyi saldırı, iyi bir savunmadır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMOR_CARROTLURE
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMOR_CARROTLURE"
msgid "I like a tight-knit bunch."
msgstr "Sıkı örülmüş bir takımı severim."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMOR_LUNARPLANT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMOR_LUNARPLANT"
msgid "This armor doesn't leaf any room for improvement."
msgstr "Bu zırhın geliştirilecek bir yaprak yeri yok."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMOR_LUNARPLANT_HUSK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMOR_LUNARPLANT_HUSK"
msgid "That'll put a thorn in your side."
msgstr "Bu sana bir diken batırır."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMOR_SANITY
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMOR_SANITY"
msgid "Wearing that makes me feel safe and insecure."
msgstr "Onu giymek bana hem güvende hem güvensiz hissettiriyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMOR_VOIDCLOTH
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMOR_VOIDCLOTH"
msgid "Oh drat, there's a tear across the front!"
msgstr "Aman, ön tarafta bir yırtık var!"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMOR_YOTH_KNIGHT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARMOR_YOTH_KNIGHT"
msgid "I'm saddled with questions."
msgstr "Sorulara binip kaldım."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARROWSIGN_PANEL.BURNT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARROWSIGN_PANEL.BURNT"
msgid "\"Don't play with matches.\""
msgstr "\"Kibritle oynama.\""

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARROWSIGN_PANEL.GENERIC
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARROWSIGN_PANEL.GENERIC"
msgid "It says \"Thataway\"."
msgstr "\"Şu yöne\" yazıyor."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARROWSIGN_PANEL.UNWRITTEN
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.ARROWSIGN_PANEL.UNWRITTEN"
msgid "The sign is currently blank."
msgstr "Tabela şu anda boş."

