msgstr "Tatlı rüyalar, kokuşmuş."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.BACKPACK
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.BACKPACK"
