msgstr "Bir yığın bozuk satranç taşı."

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CHESSJUNK2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.CHESSJUNK2"
